    ]
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "The idea began with Posting Card in 2024"
   },
   {
    "type": "video",
    "mp4": "/projects/arena-frame/683eb43a8169cc45418a3194__MConvertereu_POSTING_CARD_HERO_1_-transcode.mp4",
    "webm": "/projects/arena-frame/683eb43a8169cc45418a3194__MConvertereu_POSTING_CARD_HERO_1_-transcode.webm",
    "poster": "/projects/arena-frame/683eb43a8169cc45418a3194__MConvertereu_POSTING_CARD_HERO_1_-poster-00001.jpg"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "A simple networked device for growing and sustaining friendships. It uses a multi-colour e-ink display to let a close group share their lives in a slower, more intentional way."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "What began as a conversation about our endless, algorithm-driven online culture became a prototype for something more hopeful - a future  where less technology can lead to deeper connection."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Developed for Future Facility — a technology-focused offshoot of Industrial facility — as a way to develop and communicate the studio’s capabilities.",
    "runs": [
     {
      "t": "Developed for "
     },
     {
      "t": "Future Facility",
      "href": "https://www.futurefacility.co.uk/about"
     },
     {
      "t": " — a technology-focused offshoot of "
     },
     {
      "t": "Industrial facility",
      "href": "https://www.industrialfacility.co.uk/"
     },
     {
      "t": " — as a way to develop and communicate the studio’s capabilities."
     }
    ]
   },
   {
    "type": "video",
    "mp4": "/projects/arena-frame/68375b8c5bbb270888db18b9_orbit-transcode.mp4",
    "webm": "/projects/arena-frame/68375b8c5bbb270888db18b9_orbit-transcode.webm",
    "poster": "/projects/arena-frame/68375b8c5bbb270888db18b9_orbit-poster-00001.jpg"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Posting Card’s display refreshes seven pigments individually to show incoming photos and messages, reminiscent of developing analog film."
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/arena-frame/683e0b4b6445204456d7f1b2_RENDERS_-_12.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "This slow refresh process naturally prevents passive consumption, ensuring each use is deliberate."
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/arena-frame/6838a5d8e8981810f6c1167f_image_622.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Most displays around us glow , demanding attention and leaving us staring at lightbulbs.",
    "runs": [
     {
      "t": "Most displays around us "
     },
     {
      "t": "glow",
      "href": "https://macwright.com/2018/08/28/glow.html"
     },
     {
      "t": ", demanding attention and leaving us staring at lightbulbs."
     }
    ]
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "In contrast, the E-ink display reflects light like a photograph, interacting with shadow and ambient light — working politely in the dark."
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/arena-frame/6838a5d872962f6e13954c22_vlcsnap-2025-05-29-19h16m16s302_1.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Posting Card lives in your space, not on your person. Its ambient nature makes our social connections present in the physical world in a more subtle way."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "This sustained presence exists somewhere between fleeting digital messages and the permanence of analog print."
   },
   {
    "type": "video",
    "mp4": "/projects/arena-frame/683de8808be076c7e5e10088_landscape-transcode.mp4",
    "webm": "/projects/arena-frame/683de8808be076c7e5e10088_landscape-transcode.webm",
    "poster": "/projects/arena-frame/683de8808be076c7e5e10088_landscape-poster-00001.jpg"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "The display is bistable - it retains images without using power, consuming energy only when updating."
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/arena-frame/6838b08190743cc03dd93adf_THREEQ.THREEQUARTER.25_1.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "This resourceful characteristic led to a dematerilised form: A single PCB, protected by a silicone case and powered by a coin cell battery."
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/arena-frame/683614b24f909025057881b7_sleeve.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "A hanging clip covers both portrait and landscape orientations."
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/arena-frame/6839dac81c06ae5210d53be2_BOTTOM_H.9-1.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "This ultralight approach is reflected by a set of simple but meaningful functions"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/arena-frame/6838b100383e60f0b4df708b_SnapInsta.to_482114559_18397654534096214_6035746930035547968_n.jpg",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "A switch lets you choose between displaying new messages from your personal network in real time, or cycling back through past ones."
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/arena-frame/6839dcc412cedfa0d8e56d73_Frame_17.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "The social network is built on a distributed, peer to peer protocol."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Private messages and photos are sent directly from friend to friend, without being used to train algorithms or tailor advertisements."
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/arena-frame/6838b08095daa185e861df77_image_627.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Today's social media is like a stream - a fast, endless timeline filled with content from people you barely know."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "You plunge your head in, swept along by algorithms designed to maximise engagement and attention, leaving you gasping for air."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Posting Card is more like tending a garden, offering a space for slower, more intentional connections to grow."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "It provides a gentler, more mindful alternative for sharing images and text with a small circle of friends who can truly be themselves, free from the pressure of likes, notifications, and read receipts. Using only a simple network structure and a handful of components."
   },
   {
