 "journey": {
  "name": "Journey",
  "credit": "Journey, 2024",
  "hero": {
   "image": "/projects/journey/677d3697eed40584d33caba4_23-p-2000.webp"
  },
  "blocks": [
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "A speculative design and research company that proposes product, behaviour and system-level interventions with the objective of tackling the single most preventable cause of death worldwide: tobacco addiction"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d4d652b645f6afac52c32_39.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Today, vapes are the most popular tool for smokers to quit..."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "However they don’t address the root cause of nicotine addiction, perpetuating it in a new medium"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Their design leads to passive and continuous use, lacking the start and end points of cigarettes"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Driven by a commercial market to deliver higher doses of nicotine in increasingly convenient packages."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "The result is a single use product containing a rechargeable battery"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "With bright colours and sweet flavours driving underage usage"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "What could a vape be if it prioritised cessation instead? If it supported you through your personal and non-linear journey to sobriety?"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d3697b0b746306564da20_1.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "a smarter vaporiser"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d369731d82d5ca3b03ec5_2.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "two pods"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d369a2c00f773626c042c_3.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "nicotine and placebo"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36978cae794c96b526b3_4.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "prototype varying each pods output"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36969dc4f65c06bcfbc0_5.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "reducing dosage automatically and comfortably"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36977120fc42d04ff7ef_6.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "charging case"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36972c7e292010c3d5ef_7.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "1. undock"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36964060a319dc04fc5c_8.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "2. flick scroll wheel to activate"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d3696811b0d3947dcf286_9.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "3. ‘smoke’ for a finite amount"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d3696d2b5d0bccdf0510d_10.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "4. conclude the activity"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36964060a319dc04fc77_11.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "mimicking the (familiar) gestural ritual of smoking"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36965226fb8ee9bad64b_12.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "connected experience"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d369717348db05944470b_13.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "setting realistic weekly goals of reducing a specific trigger"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d3696fb04c28efe70f7eb_14.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "scroll wheel increases in resistance during target trigger times and locations to nudge adherence,"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36996abb75fc151fbea1_15.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "addressing both the chemical dependency and behavioural aspects of addiction"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d3697018937c1b704a33c_16.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "through digital and physical interventions"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36987f49ae2890609afd_17.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "in an enduring and desirable form"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36973722acaac22295ac_18-1.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "that wears in physically and algorithmically to its user"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36967f49ae2890609a35_19.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "ensuring they feel proud in their initiative towards a healthier future"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d369600c77c61509b96f9_20.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "always-present ambient display"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d3697d45b959d82d6a2bb_21.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "growing and wilting based on goal adherence (feedback)"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d3696af32e360a46ab6f0_22.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "the day you quit smoking"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d4ea0f5fe179642766f2c_23.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "a brand that aligns with cultural trends towards wellbeing and healthier lifestyle choices rather than the clinical nature of current medical interventions"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d369721afa0231e0b7d39_25.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "marketing that promotes quitting first, with the product as a means to the goal"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d3696af32e360a46ab624_29.svg",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/journey/677d36987120fc42d04ff968_31.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "research process"
   }
  ],
