 "stereophones": {
  "name": "Stereophones",
  "credit": "Stereophones, 2023",
  "hero": {
   "image": "/projects/stereophones/6787e877520166cdaea1e4cf_0.webp"
  },
  "blocks": [
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Touch controls on headphones disrupt the experience of enjoying music."
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "They’re objects we don't use in front of our eyes, so why apply the same swiping gestures as handheld devices?"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "This project explores a more intuitive alternative..."
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/stereophones/6787e57137bf5c2f3ddf9b40_1.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Initial research into media controls on physical audio products (semiotics, layout, heritage)"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/stereophones/67b20830db9ff326a068717b_knob.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "the familiar volume knob"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/stereophones/6787e570fbe59fdabb45ecc2_3.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Made from a motor , magnet and hall effect sensor (a really precise compass)"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "all talking together to create depth through haptic behaviours"
   },
   {
    "type": "video",
    "mp4": "/projects/stereophones/67879ab57d5f400c0387e6bf_LEFT-transcode.mp4",
    "webm": "/projects/stereophones/67879ab57d5f400c0387e6bf_LEFT-transcode.webm",
    "poster": "/projects/stereophones/67879ab57d5f400c0387e6bf_LEFT-poster-00001.jpg"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "off/on volume (with resistance at higher levels)"
   },
   {
    "type": "video",
    "mp4": "/projects/stereophones/67879e7629184de8cd5d8e09_RIGHT-transcode.mp4",
    "webm": "/projects/stereophones/67879e7629184de8cd5d8e09_RIGHT-transcode.webm",
    "poster": "/projects/stereophones/67879e7629184de8cd5d8e09_RIGHT-poster-00001.jpg"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "snapping between play/pause and spring loaded song skips"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "these tactile media controls can be used blindly and intuitively"
   },
   {
    "type": "video",
    "webm": "/videos/orbit.webm"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "magic earcups"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/stereophones/6787e59118eb58de5000cd88_4.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "gently held by replaceable branches"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/stereophones/6787e573fc8dedc507c25faa_5.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "housing batteries, the first point of failure"
   },
   {
    "type": "video",
    "mp4": "/projects/stereophones/6787ebd4618033e124b76990_Explode-transcode.mp4",
    "webm": "/projects/stereophones/6787ebd4618033e124b76990_Explode-transcode.webm",
    "poster": "/projects/stereophones/6787ebd4618033e124b76990_Explode-poster-00001.jpg"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Inviting the same communities that modify and restore vintage hifi to extend the lifespan of the product"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "purely through the allure of its experience"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/stereophones/6787e571d9e2d21cee91b7c6_7.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/stereophones/6787e571978c3844c48a67ba_8.webp",
    "size": "small"
   },
   {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "serviceable (test points, large component packages, well-supported microcontrollers)"
   },
   {
    "type": "image",
    "src": "/projects/stereophones/6787e5735f2d9d26d0e1caca_9.webp",
    "size": "large"
   },
